{
  "stem": "12255.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And of course, I must mention this, that I wasn't alone.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Where they came from exactly, I received the help of a young Jewish woman who was-- had been with a Quaker team.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And she left her team, which had gone deeper into Germany, and she offered her services to me.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And a Polish-French rabbi who had served with the French-- Polish Army in France and had been a prisoner of war, and he came.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And we formed a kind of a threesome, and we worked together and-- looking after these people.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And so, they were transferred and settled down there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And [?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Yossele ?] [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Rosensaft ?] and the other leaders began to emerge.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "They started a school.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Even later on, after I'd left, I think, it came to fruition.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "They started a theatre.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "They had adult classes, and not just for-- for religious.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "They-- they-- they survivors were not necessarily religious.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "In fact, I think most of them were not terribly religious.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "There were the religious groups, but in the main, they were left wing and not particularly interested in religious matters.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I think-- I think because the idea of-- of the land of Israel, now, was the answer to them, after what they had suffered, and were afraid they might suffer in any other country.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They wanted to have a homeland of their own.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'm sure that was the motivation.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't think there were--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think women-- women have got more guts, in some respect, than men.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- and they have more feeling-- I don't know-- for the future, or what.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I-- really, I-- I'm not into being able to answer that question.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But as a fact, I think the statistics will show that more women survived.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
